Even though we know Jaha'uva loves us, at times we may wonder where we personally fit in the

00:16:56.970 --> 00:17:05.130
congregation, especially if we can't do as much as we used to. In this video, note how three

00:17:05.130 --> 00:17:11.849
regular pioneers came to appreciate their cherished place in Jaha'uva's family, despite

00:17:11.849 --> 00:17:32.789
major changes in their lives. Shortly after getting baptized, I set the goal of becoming a regular

00:17:32.789 --> 00:17:42.279
pioneer. Then I went to preach an unassigned territory where mosquito is spoken. After that,

