I started serving as a special pioneer, and sometime later I went to the school for

00:17:48.259 --> 00:17:56.259
kingdom evangelizers. Sometime ago, I began to suffer from kidney failure, so it felt like I

00:17:56.259 --> 00:18:04.900
wasn't doing anything anymore, and I couldn't go back in time. I grew up in a Christian family.

00:18:05.700 --> 00:18:10.579
My dad worked in the construction of the Bethel branch, and then served as a Bethel I for some time.

00:18:12.420 --> 00:18:18.019
My mom was a regular pioneer when she was younger. She also volunteered at Bethel,

00:18:20.089 --> 00:18:26.650
and that's how she met my dad. Some years ago, I started suffering from severe anxiety attacks,

00:18:27.450 --> 00:18:33.849
and that really affected me in the congregation. I started to compare myself to others,

00:18:33.930 --> 00:18:39.690
and I did the same with my parents. I felt I could never live up to their example.

00:18:42.470 --> 00:18:49.670
I grew up in a family where I wasn't made to feel. I never really felt adequate.

00:18:51.269 --> 00:18:58.460
I felt so worthless. I felt very alone. When my health problems began,

