of inadequacy or dwell on the perfection that I used to demand from myself. I discovered I have

00:21:43.799 --> 00:21:50.119
something good to give to the congregation. The brothers need the good deeds that we're able to do.

00:21:53.109 --> 00:21:57.430
It gives me a lot of joy to see that I can help others overcome their trials.

00:22:00.839 --> 00:22:05.160
Then this really helps me understand that I do have a role in the congregation.

